                Modicia Alexan<supplied reason="lost">dria vixit</supplied> <lb n="2"/>annis LV Anton<supplied reason="lost">ius <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/>Lucianus cornicula<supplied reason="lost">rius co</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>hortis matri pii<supplied reason="lost">ssi</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>mae faciendum <supplied reason="lost">curavit</supplied> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>oc</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>onumentum</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eredem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>on</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>equetur</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(C): Antonius Lucianus als Ehemann bezeichnet. Es handelt sich um die cohors I Claudia Sugambrorum veterana equitata oder die cohors I Raetorum equitata.</p>
